Extension opAudioPlayer for eZ publish


Requirements
============
See the README file

Installing the extension
========================
1. Download the package.
2. Copy the downloaded package into the 'extension' directory of your
   eZ publish installation.
3. Unpack the files in the distribution.
4. Enable the extension in eZ publish.
   Regenerate the extensions autoloads config if enabling the extension by hand.
5. Clear the caches for the administration interface
6. Install AudioPlayer package
7. Configure File attribute in the Audio/Flash Player content class (Setup > Classes > Medias > Audio/Flash Player)
   to set-up the default Audio Player
8. Create an Audio Player content and pickup the vue of the audio player in the File options.
9. Have fun !!!


Troubleshooting
===============
For any problem or question, please post on the extension forums on projects.ez.no
